          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Your trusted partner for certified baby products from China. 
            We specialize in safety gates, strollers, and high chairs with full OEM/ODM support.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <a
              href="https://wa.me/8617681128186"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"
